NetHack 5.0.0 is a version of the game NetHack released in May 2026.

This package can safely be installed alongside Slackware's system default copy of NetHack.

The working directory is /var/lib/nethack500.

This script is set to build with TTY, QT, and X11 support.
(The .desktop file uses QT)
You can run in a windowed mode with 'nethack -wqt' or 'nethack -wx11'
(Commands are included to build for QT, or X11, or neither.)
